short_description: The existence of ghosts is a real phenomenon. Scientific research, historical evidence and first-hand accounts prove that our souls are consciousness with or without the physical body. Doctors discuss what happens upon death.

facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ['"Ghosts and the Afterlife," the first truly scientific investigation into ghosts and life after death, has been awarded Best Documentary Film of 2022 at the Tarzana International Film Festival, which festival took place immediately after the film\'s highly-successful premiere screening at the Regal Theatres in Los Angeles. It has also been nominated for best documentary film by two other festivals.Hollywood Picture Studios is now preparing "Ghosts and the Afterlife" for submission to the Academy Awards.', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt5748880/trivia/?ref_=tt_dyk_trv'], 'Quotes': ['On-camera narrator: With all this in mind, what is our material world made of, and how does the human soul manifest itself in this world or in any other dimension?', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt5748880/quotes/?ref_=tt_dyk_qu']}
